Galleon Insider Ring Figure Craig Drimal to Plead Guilty, Court Clerk Says

-- B y   P a t r i c i a   H u r t a d o
-- 
2011-04-26T13:46:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-26/galleon-insider-trading-defendant-drimal-to-plead-guilty-court-clerk-says.html
Craig Drimal, one of a group of
defendants charged with  insider trading  related to the Galleon
Group LLC hedge fund investigation, is scheduled to plead guilty
today in Manhattan federal court, a court clerk said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
